snippet.title: Game & Watch - Blackjack (c)1985 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
Again emulation by algestam
This time the artwork was provided by hydef, and shows the full case.  hydef's artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
This is another Game & Watch that never got officially ported by Nintendo, and didn't even get any fan remakes.  This is the first time it has been emulated.  It's a simple Blackjack game, a departure from the usual Nintendo Game & Watch material.
